people are still suffering a
great deal.

37:30.482 --> 37:33.918 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And, just
quickly, we know there was some
criticism of Ms. Suu Kyi and

37:33.918 --> 37:39.090 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
some of the things that she and
her party did during this
campaign. That seems to be

37:39.090 --> 37:43.361 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
