41:21.112 --> 41:23.915 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And we turn now, as always, to
Amy Walter of The Cook Political
Report and Tamara Keith

41:23.915 --> 41:25.983 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
