42:08.626 --> 42:10.361 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Is it working?

42:10.361 --> 42:13.297 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH, National Public
Radio: It's free media. That's
for sure.

42:13.297 --> 42:18.302 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And Hillary Clinton's campaign
